text: Uladzimir Ignatik and David Marrero were the defending champions but decided not to participate. Third seeds Tomasz Bednarek and Andreas Siljeström defeated Grégoire Burquier and Romain Jouan 6–4, 6–7(4), [14–12] in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==External links== * Main Draw Open Prevadies Saint-Brieuc - Doubles 2011 Doubles
